      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is a solid and functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation on a budget! While it shows some honest wear and tear consistent with its age and mileage, it remains a hardworking car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Perfect for a daily commuter or a first-time driver!",
