      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and the interior still smells brand new! I'm really sad to let it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. It runs like an absolute dream. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
